message.body: Is it okay if mike is in your room? He wants to do homework but I don't have a desk :(
On the bus :) Thank you for everything, darling. I love you so so much. Have good day! Call you later!
Good good! Get a seat to yourself and let your nostrils clear!!!!! Meanwhile...I eat a cookie ehhhhheheheheh!
I love you too! So so so so so so much!
Haha enjoy!! No seat to myself but comfy enough.
Boooo!!!!!
Haha maybe just kidding...dude just moved. This bus is interesting haha. Very clearly filled with europeans on holiday.
HAH! Awesome sauce!!!!!
Cant say im not a fan :)
Haha. I am and I'm not even on it! Are they British european?
Haha oooof course thats where your mind goes :-p One british girl directly behind me, but the rest im having trouble with. Belgian maybe and some kind of balkan
Whoaaaa! Impressive!
Im surrounded! But i cant figure it out! Normally good at this game
I'm sure you'll find out by the end of the ride!
Mm dont know haha. Theres a huge group of them so no need to make friends with me :-p
Then just eavesdrop :D
Oyyy. I'm dying. Didn't get coffee this morning and I'm slowly dying! Haha.
Nonono! Get coffee, even if only a small cup. Dont die, my love.
No. Neverrr! Gotta save my monies.
:) Ok. Theeeen, stay awake! You can do it!
Bahhhhumbug! I wanna go home and sleep!
It's not even like I had a bad night sleep.
Oh i know. And you will. Getting home at 2ish isnt so bad. You'll be A-ok. Hows your back?
Still a little stiff, but getting better. How are you without your headphones? Surviving?
No biggie. Dont feel like music anyway. Just spacey. The bus is quiet so not so bad.
Oh good good good!
